{"tid":2428528,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恭喜中國！法國大城市開始撤除華為通訊設備","createTime":"2021-03-01T15:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T03:49:32.000Z","uid":337052,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"35c7ce9d9f7b40dfd5b3c50f185ab476865eb9f9","tid":2428528,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:23:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">排除華為！法國大城市開始撤除華為通訊設備</span></strong><br />\n2021/03/01 21:21<br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2021/03/01/php98569t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2021%2F03%2F01%2Fphp98569t.jpg&h=fe693f2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前法國包括Altice Europe旗下的法國第2大電信商「SFR」、布依格電信（Bouygues Telecom）等通訊業者，已開始撤除法國大城市的華為無線通訊設備。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕法國藉限制電信業者執照的措施，逐步排除華為設備，<span class=\"red\">而目前法國包括Altice Europe旗下的法國第2大電信商「SFR」、布依格電信（Bouygues Telecom）等通訊業者，已開始撤除法國大城市的華為無線通訊設備。</span><br />\n<br />\n《彭博》今（1）報導，有消息人士表示，除法國偏遠地區以外，法國的電信業者已開始撤除該國大城市如土魯斯（Toulouse）、土倫（Toulon）、雷恩（Rennes）、布雷斯特（Brest）等的華為4G無線通訊設備，因為華為設備和其他供應商的5G設備不相容。知情人士表示，拆除工作始於今年初，當時法國憲法委員會（Constitutional Council）簽署了1項裁定，其迫使電信商拆除人口稠密、正升級成5G網路地區的華為設備。<br />\n<br />\n對於此報導，Altice、布依格電信均拒絕發表評論，華為尚未發表評論。不過，<span class=\"red\">布依格電信曾在去年表示，該公司必須在2028年之前，從3000座電訊塔上拆除華為設備</span>，並用愛立信設備取代，Altice則正將設備切換成Nokia。知情人士表示，有些華為設備可以轉移到有政府豁免的地區，但有些必須報廢。<br />\n<br />\n而法國其他電信商如Orange和伊里亞德（Iliad SA），則是使用Nokia和愛立信的設備。<br />\n<br />\n法國國家資訊系統安全局（ANSSI）在去年稱，將允許電信商在3年至8年的執照許可下，使用包括華為在內的設備，但若使用華為5G設備的電信營運商執照過期，便不能更新執照。不過，<span class=\"red\">華為仍在去年於法國巴黎開設了研究中心，華為並曾於去年12月表示，將在2023年於法國東部的布呂馬（Brumath），開設其在中國境外的首家生產工廠。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3452984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3452984&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1195pAf34VZm09NJx5vbAww%3D&h=783cedd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3452984&h=a42ea57d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3452984</a>"},{"pid":"89cf049b570cb8ec4d4c35b04d32efe56b8257cc","tid":2428528,"uid":279938,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"法國紅酒準備禁止出口中國"},{"pid":"244d7a47fbc1b971bba112a3cdc7bfe3d0d3ddf6","tid":2428528,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"支joke<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce23044a57d2c2fbebaef5b07982f12c9e1deec6","tid":2428528,"uid":2054,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F184142_116e4ab2cc9bd5df406a214afa33b89f.png&amp;h=88fb0d65&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"e2b9ec62b8d45a42d9dfb6379ab2bb9e8f03eded","tid":2428528,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89cf049b570cb8ec4d4c35b04d32efe56b8257cc","tid":2428528,"uid":279938,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"法國紅酒準備禁止出口中國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f477a8966638677c9cf4702e5f3774f2fcd157","tid":2428528,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T00:44:30.000Z","msg":"法國好波"},{"pid":"66a5ba5a51e238017ba6c76d752d1799940128c3","tid":2428528,"uid":53026,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"89cf049b570cb8ec4d4c35b04d32efe56b8257cc","tid":2428528,"uid":279938,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"法國紅酒準備禁止出口中國"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":